  "text": "Seeded scaffolds were labeled in vitro with BrdU (16 ng/mL/d, Sigma) for 3 days as described. [CITATION_1] 17 TUNEL staining was performed and evaluated as described. 15 Cells containing dark nuclear BrdU staining were considered to be BrdU ϩ and to have undergone DNA synthesis during labeling. Overall proliferation and apoptosis data were obtained by counting the number of BrdU ϩ and TUNEL ϩ cells out of the total cell number in histological sections.",
